comments: Ayton (PHX) and Embiid (PHI) mutually engage in marginal arm to arm contact off ball prior to disengaging.
Bridges (PHX) makes incidental hand on ball contact with Embiid (PHI) during his driving shot attempt.
Booker (PHX) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Hill (PHI) legally contests Paul's (PHX) jump shot attempt.
Ayton (PHX) maintains a legal guarding position during Embiid's (PHI) driving shot attempt.
Thybulle's (PHI) momentum carries him into Booker (PHX) at the end of the drive but the body contact is marginal.
Ayton's (PHX) arm is moving into a legal position when it makes marginal contact to Embiid's (PHI) off arm during his driving shot attempt.
Bridges (PHX) establishes himself in a legal position in Thybulle's (PHI) path and he absorbs the oncoming contact during the pick.
Hill (PHI) legally contests Paul's (PHX) jump shot attempt.
Green (PHI) makes contact with the ball during Ayton's (PHX) shot attempt near the rim.
Thybulle (PHI) places two hands on Booker (PHX) attempting to commit a take foul.
Booker (PHX) reaches in and makes contact with the ball as Embiid (PHI) begins his dribble.
Booker (PHX) legally contests Embiid's (PHI) jump shot attempt.
Hill (PHI) commits a take foul on Booker (PHX).
Bridges (PHX) legally contests Korkmaz's (PHI) jump shot attempt.
Maxey (PHI) commits a take foul on Paul (PHX).
